# Raspberry Pi 4 as Desktop Computer

=> ../img/pi4.jpg

## Hardware
- CPU overclocked to 2GHz
- 4GB RAM
- 2.5" SSD 64GB drive (USB3)
- No SDCARD

## Software
- Raspberry OS
- Remmina (VNC/RDC)
- Chrome removed, Firefx installed
- Kate - Advanced Text Editor
- LOVE2D Framework

## Usage

Raspberry Pi is perfect hardware for a slim client setup. All it needs to do is connect to VPN and run Remmina session(s). And that's nothing for a Pi4 powerful SoC.

